 ============
 = IRC Arcs =
 ============

A simple visualization of IRC communication behavior: Who is talking to whom? 
Or, more appropriately: Who is namedropping whom?

Created in late 2006, resurrected in 2011 for a lazy Sunday datavis session.
Written in Java, with the Processing library as only dependency.

Example output:
http://mardoen.textdriven.com/irc_arcs/
http://www.visualcomplexity.com/vc/project.cfm?id=403

